## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online sources, which may not encompass the full spectrum of perspectives on the topic. Additionally, the sources used may have inherent biases, as they are primarily opinion-based essays and articles. Further research, including peer-reviewed studies and expert interviews, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the reasons for supporting abortion.